text: Obraztsovoye () is a rural locality (a selo) in Ayryumovskoye Rural Settlement of Giaginsky District, Adygea, Russia. The population was 361 as of 2018. There are 3 streets.Карта села Образцовое в Республике Адыгее == Geography == The village is located on the Ayrym River. == References == Category:Rural localities in Giaginsky District
title: Obraztsovoye
